window.bookSummaryJSON = "Sara Pennypacker has earned a solid fan base for her energetic Clementine books, which feature good humor and clever wordplay. <p>Third-grader Clementine constantly has brilliant ideas popping into her brain, but sometimes they get her into trouble. Only a few people really understand her - her parents, of course, and her favorite teacher, Mr. D'Matz.</p> <p>When he receives an opportunity to do research in Egypt, Clementine hatches a plan to keep him at her school - but as usual, it doesn't quite work out the way she wants.</p>"; 
